# @beep-it/checkout-widget - AI Coding Rules

## Quick Integration Pattern
```tsx
import { CheckoutWidget } from '@beep-it/checkout-widget';

<CheckoutWidget
  publishableKey="beep_pk_..."  // REQUIRED - browser-safe only
  labels={{ scanQr: "Scan to pay" }}  // REQUIRED
  assets={[{ name: "Product", price: "9.99" }]}  // REQUIRED
  primaryColor="#007bff"  // optional theming
/>
```

## Essential Rules
- Import: `import { CheckoutWidget } from '@beep-it/checkout-widget'`
- Security: ONLY use `beep_pk_*` keys (publishable), NEVER `beep_sk_*` (secret)
- Assets: Mix `{ assetId, quantity }` (existing) or `{ name, price }` (new products)
- Styling: Inline only - no CSS imports needed
- Framework: React 18+, works with Next.js/Vite/CRA

